WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
There's a list on your computer right now
that you haven't touched in weeks.

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:08.500
Not because you're busy.

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:12.000
Because rejection is exhausting.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:18.800
