following up with a referral you don't want to pressure,

00:00:18.800 --> 00:00:24.500
or reaching out to a homeowner who's already
frustrated with the process...

00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:28.000
most agents would rather find something else to do.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:31.200
And the list just sits there.

00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:36.600
The agents consistently turning those contacts
into conversations aren't tougher than you.

00:00:36.600 --> 00:00:40.300
They just don't make those calls themselves anymore.

00:00:40.300 --> 00:00:44.600
Your Bloomie works whatever list you're building,
every single day.

00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:47.400
No hesitation. No avoidance.

00:00:47.400 --> 00:00:54.400
Trained on the objection frameworks and conversation scripts
top listing agents use to turn cold contacts into real opportunities.

00:00:54.400 --> 00:00:58.000
By the time it reaches you,
someone is actually ready to talk.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:03.400
Book a demo. We'll show you a live Bloomie
working a real prospecting list,

00:01:03.400 --> 00:01:06.600
and walk you through exactly how it gets built
for your market.

00:01:06.600 --> 00:01:09.000
Thirty minutes.

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:12.000
See how this works for you.
